# Polymarket Surge Rules
# Updated: 2026-06-14 - Complete domain coverage
# Usage: RULE-SET,https://raw.githubusercontent.com/underdog376/surge-rules/main/polymarket.list,🇭🇰HK

# === Core domains (covers all subdomains) ===
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,polymarket.com

# === WebSocket real-time data ===
# ws-api.polymarket.com, rtds endpoints — already covered by DOMAIN-SUFFIX above

# === External data/infra partners ===
# Goldsky (on-chain data indexing, Turbo Pipelines)
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,goldsky.com

# === Wallet / blockchain infra ===
# WalletConnect relay (wallet connection)
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,walletconnect.com

# === Notes ===
# polymarket.com DOMAIN-SUFFIX covers: www, clob, gamma-api, data-api,
# ws-api, static, legacy-docs, docs, builders — all subdomains
# polygon-rpc.com is NOT included (general Polygon RPC, not Polymarket-specific)
